<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Makhasa Nursery on emsenn.net</title><link>https://emsenn.net/tags/makhasa-nursery/</link><description>Recent content in Makhasa Nursery on emsenn.net</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 May 2020 09:20:21 -0400</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://emsenn.net/tags/makhasa-nursery/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>2020-05-03 Sunday</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/ecology/domains/projects/domains/makha-sa-nursery-website-2020/domains/2020/domains/05/03/</link><pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/ecology/domains/projects/domains/makha-sa-nursery-website-2020/domains/2020/domains/05/03/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="timestamp-wrapper"&gt;&lt;span class="timestamp"&gt;&amp;lt;2020-05-03 Sun 18:02&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-elisp" data-lang="elisp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;;; emsenn&amp;#39;s land management elisp&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;;; (elme)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(require &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;ht&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;;; data&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(setq elme-catalog (ht-create))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;;; functions&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-add-specimen! (id info)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; (ht-set! elme-catalog id info))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-get-specimen (id)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; (ht-get elme-catalog id))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-get-specimen-attribute (id attr)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; (ht-get (ht-get elme-catalog id) attr))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-get-specimen-species (id)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; (elme-get-specimen-attribute id &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;species&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;;; examples&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-add-specimen! &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; (ht (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;species&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;foobar&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-get-specimen &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-get-specimen-attribute &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;species&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-get-specimen-species &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>2020-05-04 Monday</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/ecology/domains/projects/domains/makha-sa-nursery-website-2020/domains/2020/domains/05/04/</link><pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/ecology/domains/projects/domains/makha-sa-nursery-website-2020/domains/2020/domains/05/04/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="timestamp-wrapper"&gt;&lt;span class="timestamp"&gt;&amp;lt;2020-05-04 Mon 08:02&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
I&amp;rsquo;m sitting outside my front door, listening to the morning birds and A Tribe Called Red, smelling the various herbs of the garden on the wind: whiffs of curry plant and thyme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More quickly than expected, the nursery has developed into a legitimate project, which has motivated me to come back to looking at how to handle its data.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>